OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,FDonald Trump has criticised Israel's
OL,7,Frecent attacks on Hezbollah as Iran
OL,8,Fmade clear the recently agreed deal
OL,9,Fwith the US was dependent on peace in
OL,10,FLebanon.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the G7 summit in France on
OL,13,FTuesday, the US president said he was
OL,14,F"not happy with the way Israel has
OL,15,Fhandled themselves with Lebanon and
OL,16,Fwith Hezbollah."
OL,18,F"They should have been able to deal
OL,19,Fwith them faster," Trump told
OL,20,Freporters.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@PO]zD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
