FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781686099
OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,FHe said the fighting had been going on
OL,7,Ftoo long and "too many people have
OL,8,Fbeen killed."
OL,10,FThe president said: "You don't have to
OL,11,Fknock down an apartment house every
OL,12,Ftime you are looking for somebody.
OL,14,F"There are a lot of people in those
OL,15,Fhouses, and they are not all
OL,16,FHezbollah, that I can tell you."
OL,18,FHe went as far as suggesting Syria
OL,19,Ftake over the disarmament of Hezbollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781686099
OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,F"I suggested to Israel to let Syria
OL,7,Ftake care of Hezbollah," Trump said.
OL,8,F"Because to be honest with you, I
OL,9,Fthink they'd do a better job."
OL,11,FSyria has a long and complicated
OL,12,Frelationship with Lebanon, with Syrian
OL,13,Ftroops maintaining a military
OL,14,Foccupation in the country from 1976 to
OL,15,F2005.
OL,17,FTrump went on to say that he's had a
OL,18,Fgreat relationship with Israeli Prime
OL,19,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu, but that
OL,20,F"Bibi has to be more responsible with
OL,21,Frespect to Lebanon".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@XO]pD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
