PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781686099
OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,F"Without us, without the United
OL,7,FStates, there would be no Israel.
OL,8,FWithout me there would be no Israel
OL,9,Fbecause no other president was willing
OL,10,Fto do what I did," he added.
OL,12,FThe criticism of Israel comes after
OL,13,FTrump finally agreed to a deal with
OL,14,FIran to end the war that the US and
OL,15,FIsrael started at the end of February.
OL,17,FAlthough the agreement has not yet
OL,18,Fbeen signed or released to the public,
OL,19,FTrump has claimed it would lead to the
OL,20,Freopening of the vital Strait of
OL,21,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
