OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,FBut on Tuesday, Iran's Foreign
OL,7,FMinister said Israel's continued
OL,8,Foccupation of southern Lebanon would
OL,9,Fviolate the deal.
OL,11,F"Without the withdrawal of Israeli
OL,12,Fforces from the territories they
OL,13,Foccupied during this war, the war has
OL,14,Fnot fully come to an end," Araghchi
OL,15,Fsaid.
