OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,FPakistan, a key mediator, has said the
OL,7,Fdeal called for an end to military
OL,8,Foperations, including in Lebanon, as
OL,9,FIran has long insisted.
OL,11,FAraghchi's call for a withdrawal is a
OL,12,Fstep further than previous calls for
OL,13,Fan end to the fighting.
OL,15,FNetanyahu said on Monday that Israel
OL,16,Fwould remain in Lebanon "as long as
OL,17,Fnecessary."
OL,26,@xD@YOUyD@KO]
