OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781686099
OL,3,CTrump criticises Israel as Iran says
OL,4,CLebanon withdrawal required for peace
OL,6,FThe discrepancy over Lebanon and
OL,7,Fseveral other thorny issues
OL,8,Funderscored how much of the agreement
OL,9,Fremains apparently unresolved ahead of
OL,10,Fa planned ceremonial signing on Friday
OL,11,Fin Geneva.
OL,13,FBut despite this, the leaders at the
OL,14,FG7 meeting in France, which included
OL,15,Fthe UK, Germany, Italy, Canada, Qatar,
OL,16,Fthe UAE and Egypt, all endorsed the
OL,17,Fagreement and were keen to see the war
OL,18,Fend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
